<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Hotel Landing Page</title>
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #fff;
      font-family: sans-serif;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #f00;
      font-size: 40px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    p {
      color: #000;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 24px;
    }

    .button {
      background-color: #00f;
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 18px;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .container {
      width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #f3f3f3;
      padding: 20px 0;
    }

    .main {
      padding: 20px 0;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #f3f3f3;
      padding: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to Our Hotel</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="main">
      <p>Our hotel is the perfect place to relax and unwind. We offer a variety of amenities, including a swimming pool, spa, and fitness center. Our rooms are spacious and comfortable, and our staff is friendly and attentive.</p>

      <p>Book your stay today and experience the difference!</p>

      <button type="button">Book Now</button>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Copyright &copy; 2023 Our Hotel</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
